{
  "stem": "22582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did-- in commercial-- commercial life, we were involved, you know, in business with all kind of Polish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But being that it was sort of very anti-Semitic [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] condition, usually Jews kept separately and-- and the Poles kept separately.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I wouldn't say-- I wouldn't say that I was-- being that I-- I am not involved with them-- with Poles, I didn't have too many-- too many occasion to be with them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you could-- during the-- whenever you met, you could feel and you could notice certain things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, personally, never had any-- any-- any-- time-- any opportunities to see it, I mean to-- by hitting or something, no.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were some-- sometimes when we were playing soccer games, for instance, or kind of games and sports games, there were very occasion that, you know, they were hitting, they were fighting, and, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- but this I wouldn't say had to be-- you could see the anti-Semitism in this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were calling names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were hitting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were always fighting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were always hitting, when-- when-- especially when Jewish team played against the other team, the Polish team.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were always-- if somebody, a Jewish would win, they were starting some kind of fights always.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always were hitting, they're always fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With-- it usually started with name-calling, and then they started fight somehow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in out sport-- in ping pong, I didn't have that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could-- because we were always so much better that nobody could-- could-- it was no contest even.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I couldn't see it even, in this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was your favorite holiday?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My favorite holiday was holiday to-- to be out of school, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- [LAUGHS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
